{"tid":1974015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛孟靜想香港人用香港錢收留1300個滯留印度的人士","createTime":"2020-04-15T14:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T07:36:37.000Z","uid":229185,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"336aa4d08c03a65a74d893b67675031e42c0563e","tid":1974015,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會議員毛孟靜接獲超過1300個滯留印度的人士求助，要求港府安排包機接回他們返港。<br />\n<br />\n在1300多宗求助個案中，逾700人是香港永久性居民，其餘是未住滿七年人士外傭，或持有工作簽證，超過半數人滯留在位於西部的旁遮普邦，其他分佈在西部的馬哈拉施特拉邦，及北部德里等21個地區。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員毛孟靜與滯留印度人士的家屬等，周四會與保安局會面，促請政府先以旁遮普邦為中心，安排包機接回滯留北部人士，再安排接回滯留南部人士，滯留人士均願意自費回港。<br />\n<br />\n滯留當地的港人家屬表示，印度最早五月上旬才解除封城令，擔心滯留當地的家人面對醫療服務短缺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=387843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387843&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=49d75f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387843&h=64044660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=387843</a>"},{"pid":"210d0242b1bdd71e80c8b6b20e1c36d13133bb77","tid":1974015,"uid":328119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"分化撚"},{"pid":"cd515beea4bf1ca76d0deeee696c290c7528476e","tid":1974015,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"210d0242b1bdd71e80c8b6b20e1c36d13133bb77","tid":1974015,"uid":328119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"分化撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"now 新聞報架屌"},{"pid":"5f1d8aa675a1a87c962771985627b35b31548c34","tid":1974015,"uid":328119,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:3